    <p>Click the <strong>RSS Feed</strong> link.</p>
<p><strong>Notes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>If you use a Firefox browser to access Canvas, you can add a Live Bookmark from this screen.</li>
<li>If you use a Safari browser to access Canvas, Safari automatically creates a RSS feed for you from this screen.</li>
</ul>
